topic: TS API Data Fetcher Bot Error
type: TS API Data Fetcher Bot Error - Process Output Node Missing

definition.text: There is a child node of type Process Output of the current node that is missing. Add this child node in order for the API Data Fetcher Bot to be able to run properly.
